Detailed Description

cvmx_srio::_tx_bell_info

This register is only updated if the BELL_ERR bit is clear in SRIO()_INT_REG. This register displays SRIO information, device ID, transaction type and priority of the doorbell transaction that generated the BELL_ERR interrupt. The register includes either a RETRY, ERROR or TIMEOUT Status.

This register is reset by the h-clock reset.
